    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this total gem. Honestly, it is in such incredible shape that you'd swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new adventure, this is definitely the one for you. I\u2019d love for you to come take a look and see just how beautiful it is in person\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
