    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS to achieve a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this chassis is exceptional: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is documented and up to date. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, tactile gate engagement, paired with a functioning variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The suspension remains tight with factory-spec bushings and dampers, preserving the original McPherson/multi-link kinematics. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation and a cabin free of bolster wear, this is a turn-key analog masterpiece for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
